<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Add genre</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Add a new genre</h1>
    <p>Is there a new genre emerging in the comic community we don't have, no worry you can add it yourself. Just fill in the form down below </p>
    
    <form action="/genres" method="POST">
        <label for="name">Genre name:</label>
        <input type="text" name="name" id="name" required >
        
         <label for="description">Genre description:</label>
        <textarea type="text" name="description" id="description"  required ></textarea>

        <button type="submit">Add genre</button>
     
    </form>
</body>
</html>